  <ul>
    <li><strong>Features</strong>: New functionality and API integrations</li>
    <li><strong>Bug Fixes</strong>: Resolved issues and improvements</li>
    <li><strong>Security Updates</strong>: Critical security patches and enhancements</li>
    <li><strong>Support</strong>: Documentation and resources for support teams</li>
  </ul>

